{{Transcript|NPC}}
{{Transcript list|Cat|Hellcat|Stray dog}}

==Overhead dialogue==
===When shooing a stray dog away===
* '''Player:''' {{overhead|Thbbbbt!}}
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Whine!}}
* {{tact|The stray dog backs away from the player.}}

===When petting a stray dog===
* '''Player:''' {{overhead|Who's a good doggy!}}
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Woof!}}
* {{tact|The stray dog follows the player around.}}

===When feeding a stray dog [[bones]]===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Woof woof!}}
* {{mes|You give the dog some nice bones.}}
* {{mes|It happily gnaws on them.}}

===When feeding a stray dog [[Raw meat|raw]] or [[cooked meat]]===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Woof woof!}}
* {{mes|You give the dog a nice piece of meat.}}
* {{mes|It gobbles it up.}}

===When feeding a stray dog [[Raw mystery meat|raw]] or [[cooked mystery meat]]===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Woof woof!}}
* {{mes|You give the dog some mystery meat.}}
* {{mes|It seem to love it, but somthing feels wrong about all of this}}

===When feeding a stray dog [[Marinated j' bones]] or [[Shaikahan bones]]===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Grrrr!}}
* {{mes|That's disgusting - you can't give it to the poor dog!}}

===When feeding a stray dog any other item===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Grrrr!}}
* {{mes|The dog doesn't seem interested in that.}}

===When interacting with a stray dog while wearing [[cat ears]]===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Bark!}}
* {{mes|He doesn't approve of your ears.}}
* {{tact|The stray dog backs away from the player.}}

===When a stray dog picks a fight with a nearby cat===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Grrr!}}
* '''Cat:''' {{overhead|Sss!}}
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Woof}}
* {{tact|The stray dog keeps barking at the cat.}}

===When a stray dog picks a fight with a nearby hellcat===
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Grrr!}}
* '''Hellcat:''' {{overhead|Sss!}}
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Woof}}
* '''Hellcat:''' {{overhead|SSSS!}}
* '''Stray dog:''' {{overhead|Whine!}}
* {{tact|The stray dog backs away from the hellcat.}}
